						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Stone in Kamatada Hola on the roa to Kōḷūr.</hi></p>						

						<p>This record in Nāgarī characters and Kannaḍa language denotes the land granted by <hi rend="bold">Buḷapa-Dēsāyi,</hi> to <hi rend="bold">Subrahmaṇyāchārya,</hi> son of <hi rend="bold">Bāḷāchārya</hi> and grandson of <hi rend="bold">Galgali Mudagallāchārya.</hi> It belongs to about the <hi rend="bold">18th century A.D.</hi></p>						

